name: End (Too)
description:
A little game i managed to throw together for LD46 with what little time i had.

The goal is to keep the egg out of harm's way, by pushing it around(as you do), with X or Z on keyboard.
You move with arrow keys ofc.

Collision detection is all over the place on this one... so don't be alarmed when you find yourself suddenly floating over lava.
